name: Arc Eden Lares
description:
Arc Eden Lares
You enter hell without checking the glowing sign
These dimly lit black circles
exuberant violence
Oh ‘neath them there rippling flesh in gold
Arising 
a sun forming silk wings
Something that begins to bellow
en masse.
eXistence [To Be]
Lonely Skies
No color no sound
Nobody hears it but I
Wickedness long gone
Now instead of eternity
Now I am
